content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 630.4 - Staffing of center

State Regulations

The center's supervisory, technical and administrative
personnel shall have the education, training and experience necessary to
effectively carry out assigned duties. To the maximum extent feasible, the
positions shall be filled by displaced homemakers. Notes
